<emphasis id="B967615F2F70FFFB4EAFF8EEFD98F8C7" bold="true" box="[199,583,1874,1899]" pageId="10" pageNumber="161">Pertinent taxonomic references.</emphasis>
Cope (1868a, 1874), Peters (1871), Boulenger (1885), Vanzolini (1961b), Dixon (1973), Duellman (1978), Kohlsdorf &amp; Wagner (2006), Freitas (2011), Teixeira 
<emphasis id="B967615F2F70FFFB4A1EF8CBFB76F823" box="[1142,1193,1910,1935]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="161">et al</emphasis>
